1
00:00:00,080 --> 00:00:04,316
QDPX is an open exchange format for qualitative projects.

2
00:00:04,316 --> 00:00:09,023
QualCanvas can export and import QDPX, which helps when work

3
00:00:09,023 --> 00:00:13,259
needs to move to or from a compatible tool.

4
00:00:13,259 --> 00:00:17,024
Always plan time to verify the round trip.

5
00:00:17,424 --> 00:00:20,777
Open the Export and import menu.

6
00:00:20,777 --> 00:00:26,366
Use QDPX for project exchange, while reports, spreadsheets and images

7
00:00:26,366 --> 00:00:28,601
serve different handoff needs.

8
00:00:28,601 --> 00:00:33,072
Save the export in an approved research location.

9
00:00:33,472 --> 00:00:38,238
For import, choose Import QDPX and select a QDPX or

10
00:00:38,238 --> 00:00:41,574
ZIP package within the displayed twenty-megabyte limit.

11
00:00:41,574 --> 00:00:46,816
Read the warning in the dialog before changing an existing canvas.

12
00:00:47,216 --> 00:00:52,781
For the first transfer, work in a copy or fresh destination canvas.

13
00:00:52,781 --> 00:00:57,418
That gives you a recoverable comparison if a source type,

14
00:00:57,418 --> 00:01:01,592
code relation or formatting detail maps differently between applications.

15
00:01:01,992 --> 00:01:06,694
After import, compare source counts, open sample excerpts and inspect

16
00:01:06,694 --> 00:01:09,046
the codebook, hierarchy and memos.

17
00:01:09,046 --> 00:01:13,748
Features that are unique to either application may not have

18
00:01:13,748 --> 00:01:17,040
a one-to-one equivalent in the exchange format.

19
00:01:17,440 --> 00:01:22,028
A QDPX package can contain participant text and analytical notes.

20
00:01:22,028 --> 00:01:26,616
Encrypt or otherwise protect it where your protocol requires, send

21
00:01:26,616 --> 00:01:31,205
it only to authorised recipients and delete temporary copies according

22
00:01:31,205 --> 00:01:33,040
to your retention plan.

23
00:01:33,440 --> 00:01:38,825
A responsible QDPX handoff includes a backup, a controlled transfer,

24
00:01:38,825 --> 00:01:43,671
structured verification and a note of anything that changed.

25
00:01:43,671 --> 00:01:49,056
The QualCanvas training centre includes separate tutorials for reports, spreadsheets

26
00:01:49,056 --> 00:01:50,672
and visual exports.
